<s-1 id="RM0000014WB00GX_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00007RB00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT SPEEDOMETER</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the operation.</ptxt>
<s3>
<ptxt>Using a speedometer tester (calibrated chassis dynamometer), check the speedometer indication according to the table below.</ptxt>
